	(text "* Using the ~{OE} pin as the input of a 74LV1T125\n  here, instead of a 74LV1T04, creates a more\n  efficient inverter since the output is Hi-Z during\n  normal operations, and is only active during\n  RESET. Also, avoids an additional\n  line item on BOM."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
